📊 Sales Data Dashboard – Excel Project
📌 Overview

This project is an interactive Sales Data Dashboard built in Microsoft Excel to analyze business performance using sales and profit data.
The dashboard transforms raw transactional data into meaningful insights through Pivot Tables, Pivot Charts, and Slicers.

##Data set used
[Download Excel Dashboard](https://github.com/LakshmiRadhikaAndluru/Excel-project1/raw/main/Copy%20of%20Sales%20Data%20Set%20for%20Dashboard.xlsm)


It helps users quickly identify:

🚚 Most used shipment modes
🏆 Top 5 profitable states
📉 Top 3 least profitable products
🌆 Top 10 most profitable cities
👥 Performance by customer segment
🛍️ Profit trends by product category

The dashboard is fully interactive, allowing users to filter results dynamically using slicers for:

Customer Segment
Product Category
Ship Mode

This enables faster decision-making and better understanding of business performance across regions, products, and logistics.

